Contributing
------------

First of all, thank you for considering contributing to this project

Did you found a bug?
--------------------

- Create a new issue
- Describe with as much detail as possible how to reproduce the issue
- Describe with as much detail as possible which should be the correct behavior

Want to contribute with documentation?
--------------------------------------

Awesome! Please create a new issue describing the piece of work you would
like to document so we can be organized on the work to be made

Want to contribute with code?
-----------------------------

Sweet! Please create a new issue describing the work you will be doing so 
we can be organized (prevent multiple people working on the same stuff)

Have fun!
